All Implemented Interfaces:
Closeable, Flushable, AutoCloseable, ExtendedDataOutputStream
public class ExtendedDataOutputStream extends LittleEndianOutputStream implements ExtendedDataOutputStream
Writes numbers in little endian format. Writes strings by first writing the stringlength and then the *bytes* of the string (no unicode support up to now)
